title: Australia.The.Story.of.Us.Part.1.Worlds.Collide.PDTV.x264-CBFM
description:
An extraordinary narrative more than 40,000 years in the making about the people, places and events which have shaped Australia from the first footprints on the continent to the present day.




Part 1: Worlds Collide

Over 40,000 years in the making comes the story about the people, places and events that have shaped our country. In 1808, Aboriginal Australians thrive and leave their mark on the driest continent on Earth.



Original Air Date: 15-Feb-2015
